"https://na.cx/i/L5kz59v.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL5kz59v.gif&h=6e4c68e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eNTYOnQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeNTYOnQ.gif&h=2d6b3e5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nr0gz2S.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnr0gz2S.gif&h=f6419a69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下午時份於金鐘天橋附近一帶，一名中年婦人向警員哭求停止對香港人使用武力，遭警員近距離以不明武器擊中頭部。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5KBLtok.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5KBLtok.gif&h=b8ae447c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n一名市民於金鐘橋底下，遭警員以布袋彈瞄準頭部射擊。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h6jQEvO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh6jQEvO.gif&h=54b6b60a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n警員向示威者投擲鐵通。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gS1GMaW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgS1GMaW.jpg&h=07ae5fa1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n男警強脫女示威者上衣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E0Lz6a5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE0Lz6a5.gif&h=34338ba4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員不斷挑釁示威者。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nMOxSRw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnMOxSRw.png&h=3bc0c0bf&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n不合理搜身程序及罰企式羞辱年青人。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">其他圖集</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ADpQExp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FADpQExp.png&h=8b63eed5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PEsOrcs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPEsOrcs.gif&h=182c1c2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真仆街 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n短片系列<br />\n香港警察粗暴對待示威者實錄<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nYV52IBKbtY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2